title: Shocker Internet Drive In Week 10 - Christmas Special

sources.title: ShockerInternetDriveInWeek10 ChristmasSpecial
sources.description: Snuggle up close, turn the heat up, visit the snack bar for some hot coco (and shrimp roll), and enjoy our special Christmas Special Presentation. After a classic 1940's "Rudolf The Red Nosed Reindeer" cartoon as well as a "Visit With Santa", we proudly offer that holiday piece of cinema poo-poo, "Santa Claus Conquers The Martians". What else can we say - Happy Holidays & Merry Christmas to all! For more information, go here - www.shockerdrivein.co.cc or http://beatlbay7900.hostoutfitter.com/home.html
